      <div class="faq-item" itemscope itemprop="mainEntity" itemtype="https://schema.org/Question">
        <h3 itemprop="name">❓ Aveti animatori familiari cu zona Crangasi?</h3>
        <div itemscope itemprop="acceptedAnswer" itemtype="https://schema.org/Answer">
          <p itemprop="text">Da — unii din animatorii nostri locuiesc in zona Crangasi, asa ca nu se vor pierde niciodata.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item" itemscope itemprop="mainEntity" itemtype="https://schema.org/Question">
        <h3 itemprop="name">❓ Sunt disponibili animatorii in Crangasi sambata dimineata?</h3>
        <div itemscope itemprop="acceptedAnswer" itemtype="https://schema.org/Answer">
          <p itemprop="text">Da — avem disponibilitate toata ziua sambata si duminica, inclusiv dimineata de la 10:00.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item" itemscope itemprop="mainEntity" itemtype="https://schema.org/Question">
        <h3 itemprop="name">❓ Puteti face si un program de botez in Crangasi?</h3>
        <div itemscope itemprop="acceptedAnswer" itemtype="https://schema.org/Answer">
          <p itemprop="text">Da — pachetul Super 7 (1290 RON) include 1 animator + 4 ursitoare pentru botez, 3 ore de program complet. Il recomandam pentru botezuri.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="sec-alt">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="cta-box">
      <h2>Rezerva animator în <span style="color:var(--primary)">Crangasi</span></h2>
      <p>⚡ Disponibilitate limitata in weekend — locurile se ocupa rapid!<br>Garantie contractuala: daca copiii nu s-au simtit bine, nu platesti!</p>
      <div class="btns" style="justify-content:center">
        <a href="tel:+40722744377" class="btn-p cta">📞 0722 744 377</a>
        <a href="https://wa.me/40722744377" class="btn-wa cta">💬 WhatsApp</a>
      </div>
      <nav class="nav-links">
        <a href="/petreceri/sector-6">← Sectorul 6</a>
        <a href="/animatori-petreceri-copii">🎭 Toate pachetele</a>
        <a href="/petreceri/bucuresti">🏙️ Animatori Bucuresti</a>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

</Layout>